subject: Basketball
lead_paragraph: D. J. Augustin scored 23 points, A. J. Abrams had 21 and No. 15 Texas shot 64 percent from the field last night in a 97-78 rout of No. 7 Tennessee in the championship game of the StubHub Legends Classic in Newark.
